profile: Since 1989, Dan Martineau Contracting has specialized in commercial and residential construction in Corner Brook and throughout the Western Newfoundland region. We are a general contractor offering many services including remodels, renovations, damage repairs, disaster reconstruction, tenant up-fits, build-outs, flooring, and more. Dan Martineau Contracting has worked hard for over three decades to earn a great reputation for superior quality and honesty in all that we do. The Dan Martineau team is made up of skilled craftsmen and respected sub-trades and is ready to handle any project you may have. We provide the highest quality craftsmanship, materials, and customer service. Referrals are definitely available.
